    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Escape From WoA: Valentine Episode",
        "Description": "On Valentine&apos;s Day, Munga ended his live stream. In the moment after blinked, Munga found himself transported to Dartmoor in WoA.\r\r&quot;If you want to return to the real world, you must complete 3 targets,&quot; said Diana.\r\rTarget No.1 \u2013 Create two explosions to cause chaos\r\rTarget No.2 \u2013 Find Phinas Whitmer, by disguising yourself as him, you can deceive the game system\r\rTarget No.3 \u2013 Find Otto Lee, the core program of the Dartmoor map. Only by eliminating him can you leave the game world\r\r&quot;Good luck.&quot;\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Atmosphere.",
